						               													<description>UeStop! is an exciting competitive word game for 2-6 player, where players test their knowledge and their reflex, struggling to be the first one to find the correct word with the correct letter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played in turns and in each turn there is a card with one of the four possible colors (green, yellow, red, blue), also showing 4 categories on four edges of the card and 4 different letters in the middle of the card. These 4 letters are presented in colored bubbles, matching the colors of the cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After all the players have read the categories and are ready, another card is opened and then, the players will try to be the first one to put their hand over the card and say one word with the starting letter indicated on the colored bubble of the second card that matches the color of the first card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the player answers correctly, she gains the card as a reward worth one point. Another turn starts and the game continues until any player gets 5 points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is the basic to play UeStop!, but the game also contains 3 new game modes that will challenge the players with new rules and adding strategy to the gameplay.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
